data.description: WELCOME TO THIS COMPLETELY UPDATED 2 BEDROOM 1 BATHROOM HOME! This home is completely move-in ready and absolutely adorable! You will fall in love as soon as you see the stunning kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and spacious enough for the chef in the family! Beautiful laminate flooring throughout too! 2 light and bright bedrooms and a nice bathroom add to the features of this home! A large private backyard adds to the appeal of this home as you do not have neighbors behind you! Shed included to store your things! Garage has been used as a separate living area, but easily converted back to a garage! COME SEE THIS HOME NOW! Roof - 2018, AC - 2018
